venue.name: HSBNE
venue.accessibility: The venue is on the ground floor and parking is available close by.
venue.under_18: At this Venue you must be accompanied by a Guardian at all times
venue.public_transport: Northshore Hamilton City Cat is right outside the venue. Please see http://hsbne.org/thespace.html for more details on transport
venue.parking: Free Parking is available on site. Please see http://hsbne.org/thespace.html for more details on transport
venue.public_transport_last:
The last ferry leaves at 11.24pm towards North Quay.
For all public transport please check [the Translink website](http://translink.com.au) for your particular service and what time the last call is.

catering:
+ We will join the main GovHack Brisbane node on the Friday evening for the launch and dinner.
+ Basic lunch will be provided each day
